game.name: Plane Tunnel
game.description:
Is not exciting to operate a plane in a blue sky thousands of miles away from the surface? And what will happen if you are allowed to fly a plane in a tunnel? Yes, we have today brought to you a brand new adventure challenge where you have to operate an aeroplane in a tunnel that is full of different kinds of obstacles. Are you ready to take on this unique kind of challenge? Join Plane Tunnel game and get ready to put your plane flying skills to test to the optimum level! 
Your objective in this cool aeroplane game is to flay plane through the tunnel while avoiding colliding with any obstacles. Do not forget to collect the coins to boost your score. The coins you collect on your way will help to upgrade your plane further. This highly addictive and endless plane game features 2 planes, and easy to understand score system. Move your plane using the AD or arrow keys and shoot with the space key!
May be you get out of ammo during the gameplay. But, do not bother as you can collect the ammo again on your path. Keep shooting and flying as long as possible to beat your high score in this one of the best html5 plane games for boys! We have a wide range of free games in the category of adventure on our website atmegame.com which does not ask you to download games. So, if this flying game does not appeal you, check out the other ones to seek fun when you are bored.
